<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="66880000t" end="75330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">真棒</p>
<p begin="78320000t" end="89950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">你真棒呢</p>
<p begin="89960000t" end="108370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">就算被拉姆以外的人说</p>
<p begin="108380000t" end="130180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">我也一点都不高兴啦</p>
<p begin="239990000t" end="251560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">太棒了</p>
<p begin="261660000t" end="271730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我就说</p>
<p begin="271740000t" end="287450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">一点都不高兴啦</p>
<p begin="318700000t" end="330470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">老姐</p>
<p begin="330480000t" end="364760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">你要在那边发呆到什么时候</p>
<p begin="364770000t" end="376810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">不, 我并不…</p>
<p begin="381420000t" end="397830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">老姐你自己应该</p>
<p begin="397840000t" end="420200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">也有被大将托付的事要做吧</p>
<p begin="420210000t" end="431150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">拜托了喔</p>
<p begin="494350000t" end="506870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">我相信你</p>
<p begin="514220000t" end="528930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">那当然</p>
<p begin="785920000t" end="809740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">看来大姐走远了啊</p>
<p begin="913800000t" end="925270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">猎肠者</p>
<p begin="967530000t" end="984440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">艾尔莎·葛兰西尔特</p>
<p begin="1004450000t" end="1033640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">圣域超强最强的盾</p>
<p begin="1039900000t" end="1058370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">加菲尔·汀泽尔</p>
<p begin="1076100000t" end="1106370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">这可是本大爷华丽的初战啊大将</p>
<p begin="1113130000t" end="1143020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">所以你那边也要好好干啊</p>
<p begin="1205950000t" end="1216810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">为什么</p>
<p begin="1224940000t" end="1245170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">我要带你出去, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="1254310000t" end="1279610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">这次我一定会手牵手</p>
<p begin="1279620000t" end="1300450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">把你拉出去沐浴阳光</p>
<p begin="1300470000t" end="1323140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">一起玩到那件洋装沾满污泥</p>
<p begin="1323150000t" end="1344620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">变成全黑为止</p>
<p begin="1352210000t" end="1379710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">你要把贝蒂从这里带出去?</p>
<p begin="1393220000t" end="1408340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">多管闲事</p>
<p begin="1412950000t" end="1442080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">谁拜托过你这么做了</p>
<p begin="1442090000t" end="1465260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">现在可是分秒必争啊</p>
<p begin="1470500000t" end="1498850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">你知道现在外面变成怎样了吗</p>
<p begin="1498860000t" end="1528540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">我知道有入侵者到宅邸里面了</p>
<p begin="1533910000t" end="1560140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">但是这里可是大精灵的禁书库</p>
<p begin="1562940000t" end="1581530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不管外面有什么威胁…</p>
<p begin="1581540000t" end="1598110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">不, 机遇门的效果</p>
<p begin="1598120000t" end="1618370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">仅限于关着的门而已</p>
<p begin="1622360000t" end="1633160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">对方也知道这件事</p>
<p begin="1633170000t" end="1669030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">为什么敌人会知道这个缺陷呢</p>
<p begin="1699900000t" end="1719300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">是罗兹瓦尔告诉他们的</p>
<p begin="1741130000t" end="1756680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">…就是这么一回事</p>
<p begin="1772000000t" end="1787740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">罗兹瓦尔的睿智之书上</p>
<p begin="1787750000t" end="1815580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">记述了贝蒂的死亡吧</p>
<p begin="1855590000t" end="1878780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">你…为什么</p>
<p begin="1878790000t" end="1892280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">要露出那种表情</p>
<p begin="1892290000t" end="1918940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">贝蒂的命运已经被订下了</p>
<p begin="1922800000t" end="1937180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">难道你的书上</p>
<p begin="1937190000t" end="1968040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">也写着会被那家伙杀掉吗</p>
<p begin="1968050000t" end="1993600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">上面什么都没有写喔</p>
<p begin="2003530000t" end="2013170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">就像至今为止一样</p>
<p begin="2013180000t" end="2035390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">贝蒂的命运只是白纸而已</p>
<p begin="2035400000t" end="2046570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">这样的话</p>
<p begin="2050170000t" end="2088250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你没有理由要按照<br />罗兹瓦尔希望的去做啊</p>
<p begin="2088260000t" end="2102380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">只要像之前那样</p>
<p begin="2102390000t" end="2132140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">由你自己决定自己想做的事就好了</p>
<p begin="2139250000t" end="2162740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">贝蒂自己决定?</p>
<p begin="2182040000t" end="2192880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">至今为止的日子</p>
<p begin="2192970000t" end="2226370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">到底有什么是贝蒂自己决定的</p>
<p begin="2236920000t" end="2270610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">照母亲吩咐守在宅邸里</p>
<p begin="2270620000t" end="2284770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">一直都是一个人…</p>
<p begin="2291490000t" end="2315150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">到底有什么是贝蒂自己决定的</p>
<p begin="2321640000t" end="2345520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">碧翠丝到底做过什么</p>
<p begin="2345530000t" end="2356120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">又是谁呢</p>
<p begin="2366130000t" end="2378460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">碧翠丝…</p>
<p begin="2383540000t" end="2406860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">贝蒂的一生只是一片空白</p>
<p begin="2412260000t" end="2423580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">完全的空白</p>
<p begin="2426450000t" end="2439230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">真的, 真的</p>
<p begin="2447830000t" end="2476490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">如果贝蒂只是一本书就好了</p>
<p begin="2492800000t" end="2521680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">但是贝蒂是有心灵的</p>
<p begin="2529260000t" end="2538440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">随着时间经过</p>
<p begin="2538450000t" end="2555180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">会去思考各式各样的事情</p>
<p begin="2555190000t" end="2563920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">不断烦恼</p>
<p begin="2563920000t" end="2582810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">最后变得什么都无法相信</p>
<p begin="2594930000t" end="2622100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我想不起母亲的微笑</p>
<p begin="2625780000t" end="2665140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">也有好几个夜晚<br />都曾尝试将记忆拼凑起来</p>
<p begin="2673420000t" end="2687780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">也曾因为孤独和恐惧</p>
<p begin="2687790000t" end="2717660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">希望能有谁陪在身边</p>
<p begin="2726220000t" end="2754250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">但最后大家都把贝蒂丢下了</p>
<p begin="2758160000t" end="2778780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">不管是母亲大人还是罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="2783090000t" end="2795480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">还有琉兹也是</p>
<p begin="2812200000t" end="2830640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">精灵碧翠丝的命运</p>
<p begin="2830650000t" end="2848290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">就是会一直孤独地活着</p>
<p begin="2848300000t" end="2874680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">最后被大家置之不理</p>
<p begin="2895060000t" end="2902160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">但是</p>
<p begin="2921550000t" end="2947270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我现在已经稍微释怀了</p>
<p begin="2968340000t" end="3000360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">如果睿知之书上面有记载贝蒂的事的话</p>
<p begin="3009740000t" end="3021560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">那就代表母亲大人</p>
<p begin="3027260000t" end="3062050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">并没有忘记贝蒂</p>
<p begin="3087290000t" end="3100870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="3111570000t" end="3127070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你是个笨蛋</p>
<p begin="3127080000t" end="3140380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">大笨蛋</p>
<p begin="3140390000t" end="3164050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">笨到让人心痛得看不下去</p>
<p begin="3164060000t" end="3171910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">什么…</p>
<p begin="3171920000t" end="3190060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">活了400年的时间</p>
<p begin="3190070000t" end="3222110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">为什么就只能得出这种极端的结论啊</p>
<p begin="3222120000t" end="3270760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">你就没想过也有可能是<br />你母亲不小心拿错书给你了吗</p>
<p begin="3270770000t" end="3292190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">你是在污辱母亲大人吗</p>
<p begin="3295630000t" end="3320610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">她有可能会犯这种愚蠢的失误吗</p>
<p begin="3320620000t" end="3342360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">你能够说百分之百不可能吗</p>
<p begin="3342370000t" end="3355720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">那么你真的相信</p>
<p begin="3355730000t" end="3400650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">一个母亲有可能<br />会给自己女儿空白的书吗</p>
<p begin="3400660000t" end="3434410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">那是…你那种讲法</p>
<p begin="3441290000t" end="3470090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">你到底想让贝蒂说些什么</p>
<p begin="3470100000t" end="3493190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">那我就说清楚一点吧</p>
<p begin="3496790000t" end="3520540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">清楚到你那笨妈妈都能够听见!</p>
<p begin="3534760000t" end="3564400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">你打算被空白的书和<br />四百年前的口头约定</p>
<p begin="3564410000t" end="3587310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">给折腾到什么时候</p>
<p begin="3587320000t" end="3625160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">你想做的事情由你自己决定, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="3637320000t" end="3649270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">已经400年了</p>
<p begin="3653330000t" end="3676200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">就算来个一次叛逆期</p>
<p begin="3676210000t" end="3696880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">应该也不为过吧</p>
<p begin="3696890000t" end="3714400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">不管你说什么</p>
<p begin="3714410000t" end="3732380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">我已经缔结了契约…</p>
<p begin="3737320000t" end="3754640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">契约是…绝对的…</p>
<p begin="3754650000t" end="3761160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">所以…</p>
<p begin="3761170000t" end="3784170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">像你这种寻找着契约的破口</p>
<p begin="3784180000t" end="3804360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">最后却因为必须遵守契约而寻死的人</p>
<p begin="3804370000t" end="3815730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">还真敢说</p>
<p begin="3822460000t" end="3845350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">如果遵守约定你就会死的话</p>
<p begin="3845360000t" end="3874520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">那么破坏约定让你活下来还比较好</p>
<p begin="3879060000t" end="3907710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我会选择这条路就这么不可思议吗</p>
<p begin="3911150000t" end="3945930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">这…这只是你固执己见的任性想法而已</p>
<p begin="3945940000t" end="3967310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">我知道我是固执己见</p>
<p begin="3967320000t" end="3986150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">也知道很任性</p>
<p begin="3989040000t" end="3996830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">不过</p>
<p begin="4003970000t" end="4029220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">重要的事物我是不会退让的</p>
<p begin="4056810000t" end="4100440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">如…如果你就是"那个人"的话</p>
<p begin="4136850000t" end="4150650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">你愿意成为</p>
<p begin="4155020000t" end="4196660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">贝蒂的…"那个人"吗</p>
<p begin="4218940000t" end="4232590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">你是笨蛋吗</p>
<p begin="4232600000t" end="4244760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">我怎么可能会</p>
<p begin="4244770000t" end="4275380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">是你那个什么来路不明的"那个人"啊</p>
<p begin="4316560000t" end="4333790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">…搞什么鬼</p>
<p begin="4340990000t" end="4355810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">那个笨蛋</p>
<p begin="4369880000t" end="4375960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">可恶</p>
<p begin="4375970000t" end="4397200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">那个急性子的萝莉</p>
<p begin="4411970000t" end="4421890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">菜月先生</p>
<p begin="4429860000t" end="4440740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你们为什么会在这里</p>
<p begin="4440750000t" end="4458380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">不是早该逃跑了吗</p>
<p begin="4458390000t" end="4469320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">是魔兽</p>
<p begin="4469330000t" end="4484850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">已经到处都是了</p>
<p begin="4484860000t" end="4497860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">是梅莉啊</p>
<p begin="4497870000t" end="4516580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">不过我们不是已经想过对策了吗</p>
<p begin="4516590000t" end="4544080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">有对这个完全免疫的魔兽</p>
<p begin="4575240000t" end="4586310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">真的吗</p>
<p begin="4586320000t" end="4597150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">为什么</p>
<p begin="4689330000t" end="4697280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">佩特拉</p>
