<p begin="15078970000t" end="15117130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">知道了那个拼命三郎<br />是怎样的心情以后</p>
<p begin="15128820000t" end="15145770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">老子对自己感到好惭愧</p>
<p begin="15154800000t" end="15173590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">那家伙还只是个14岁的孩子啊</p>
<p begin="15179410000t" end="15194630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">即使如此, 他还是像那样…</p>
<p begin="15208000000t" end="15218810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">那孩子非常了不起</p>
<p begin="15231230000t" end="15242790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">还有爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="15248870000t" end="15273560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">您也同样了不起</p>
<p begin="15277480000t" end="15303150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">所以就让我们在此见证到最后吧</p>
<p begin="15363480000t" end="15372460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">我知道了</p>
<p begin="15378370000t" end="15395710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">我一定会平安完成试炼</p>
<p begin="15395720000t" end="15405320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">那个时候</p>
<p begin="15405330000t" end="15421520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">我们再来好好谈一谈吧</p>
<p begin="15434120000t" end="15451260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">好的, 约好了</p>
<p begin="15455170000t" end="15461260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">一定…</p>
<p begin="15474200000t" end="15494760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">太长又太严肃了啦</p>
<p begin="15494770000t" end="15522370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">而且中间还从"我"变回了"老子"</p>
<p begin="15522380000t" end="15538710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">真是丢人, 丢人</p>
<p begin="15538720000t" end="15559510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">对, 对不起, 长老</p>
<p begin="15576260000t" end="15584880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">无论如何</p>
<p begin="15584890000t" end="15610240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">老朽们的意见就像刚刚那样</p>
<p begin="15610250000t" end="15620980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">这样就…</p>
<p begin="15631140000t" end="15641760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">怎么了吗</p>
<p begin="15656590000t" end="15683680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">那个…我刚刚听到琉兹</p>
<p begin="15683690000t" end="15708370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">被称呼为长老</p>
<p begin="15716530000t" end="15728070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">有点吓了一跳</p>
<p begin="15790210000t" end="15812290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">总觉得有些无法释怀</p>
<p begin="15831560000t" end="15840570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">不过还是谢谢</p>
<p begin="15850210000t" end="15866910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">我感觉自己能够更加努力了</p>
<p begin="15871520000t" end="15902190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">能帮上你的忙就太好了</p>
<p begin="15911830000t" end="15941150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">下一关就是最后的试炼了吧</p>
<p begin="15951750000t" end="15965950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">我打算马上再去挑战</p>
<p begin="15969950000t" end="15992340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">不过…琉兹</p>
<p begin="15992350000t" end="16007570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">你知道拉姆去哪里了吗</p>
<p begin="16015730000t" end="16047530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">拉姆似乎有一个无法抽身的使命</p>
<p begin="16047540000t" end="16058340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">使命</p>
<p begin="16076140000t" end="16101780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">爱蜜莉雅大人做好爱蜜莉雅该做的</p>
<p begin="16101790000t" end="16117290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">拉姆会做好拉姆该做的</p>
<p begin="16117300000t" end="16137040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">然后一起达成各自的使命吧</p>
<p begin="16137050000t" end="16148000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">她是这么说的</p>
<p begin="16245140000t" end="16263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">那么, 我出发了</p>
<p begin="16301710000t" end="16320570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">-小心喔<br />-祝您武运昌隆</p>
<p begin="16407720000t" end="16433380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">面对迟早会到来的灾厄吧</p>
<p begin="16470260000t" end="16500470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">(映照在水面上的幸福)</p>
</div>
